headline: 2 AI Stocks Down More Than 45% to Buy in March
summary: Much of that slide took place after an SEC filing revealed that AI chip leader Nvidia had sold its stake in the small company.  SoundHound's top line nearly doubled in 2024, which partially reflects the additional revenue that came from its acquisition of Amelia.
